title: Ericsson third-quarter operating profit lags forecasts

Ericsson third-quarter operating profit lags forecasts 
Reuters Friday 23rd October, 2015 
Swedish mobile telecom equipment maker Ericsson posted third-quarter sales and operating profit below market expectations on Friday, weighed down by its key networks unit....
